  "detailed_description": "You play Hector the Cat a Treasure Hunter.<br />\r\nExplore Silver Island 's Dungeons to gather as many Treasure as you Can and become the Best Treasure Hunter.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGameplay:<br />\r\n- Run are short  ( < 45 mn)  and  Last 10 days <br />\r\n- For each run Maps and Dungeons are randomly generated<br />\r\n- Dungeons are rated from 1 stars to 3 stars related to their difficulty<br />\r\n- Switch Between Guns and Sword to adapt fighting situation<br />\r\n- Improve your competence  or buy  new one when Lvl UP;<br />\r\n- Construct the adapt Build ( Sword/Gun/Magic) to evolve;<br />\r\n- Buy specific armor and consumable  to improve your chance to defeat Boss and succeed the most difficult dungeon<br />\r\n- You get a rank in accordance with you skill at the end of each run.<br />\r\n- Die and retry to improve your skills<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCould you be the best Hunter and get the S rank ?",
  "about_the_game": "You play Hector the Cat a Treasure Hunter.<br />\r\nExplore Silver Island 's Dungeons to gather as many Treasure as you Can and become the Best Treasure Hunter.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGameplay:<br />\r\n- Run are short  ( < 45 mn)  and  Last 10 days <br />\r\n- For each run Maps and Dungeons are randomly generated<br />\r\n- Dungeons are rated from 1 stars to 3 stars related to their difficulty<br />\r\n- Switch Between Guns and Sword to adapt fighting situation<br />\r\n- Improve your competence  or buy  new one when Lvl UP;<br />\r\n- Construct the adapt Build ( Sword/Gun/Magic) to evolve;<br />\r\n- Buy specific armor and consumable  to improve your chance to defeat Boss and succeed the most difficult dungeon<br />\r\n- You get a rank in accordance with you skill at the end of each run.<br />\r\n- Die and retry to improve your skills<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCould you be the best Hunter and get the S rank ?",
